$interpreted: Dylan: Show me what you've got.

Todd: What in the world is the Royal Infantry doing,
having this dork wandering outside the bedroom?
Todd: How's his Majesty Theodore going to sleep with all this constant noise?
Dylan: Has His Majesty not been sleeping well recently?
Todd: You're only hearing about it now?
Dylan: But it's part of the Royal Infantry's duty to patrol outside the master bedroom.
Todd: I don't give a damn about...
Todd: Someone~ someone come protect His Majesty!
Todd: Your Majesty! Your Majesty! Forget chasing the guy! Royal Infantry! Follow and protect his Majesty!
